        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-900">
            Capital & Fundraising Support
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-900 mb-4">
            We help structure the story behind your numbers, from financial
            modeling to deck-ready metrics and scenario planning.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-primary-900">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Image
